            "title": "盤中速報 - 京晨科(6419)股價拉至漲停，漲停價98.0元，成交481張",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>京晨科(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6419:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6419\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6419-TW</a>)01日11:05上漲8.9元，股價漲停報98.0元，委買295,000張，成交481張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主要業務為數位監控系統。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>京晨科(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6419:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6419\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6419-TW</a>)近5日股價上漲10.14%，櫃買市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>下跌1.6%，股價漲幅表現優於大盤。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+137 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+138 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：-1 張</li> <li>融資增減：+68 張</li> <li>融券增減：0 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
